author: Natasha Patel
title: Priyanka Chopra’s New Magazine Cover Is Everything
text:
A post shared by Marie Claire (@marieclairemag) on Mar 13, 2017 at 5:30am PDT 
God damn, she’s done it again. Another month, another magazine cover… Priyanka Chopra is a woman on a mission and seems like there’s just no stopping—Or pausing or just good ol’ relaxing. Now of course, it is understandable if you have an agenda of being on the April cover for Marie Claire . 
Dressed in Gucci, with a studded shoulder vest, this Baywatch babe is a sight for sore eyes! A post shared by Marie Claire (@marieclairemag) on Mar 13, 2017 at 7:38am PDT 
With more pictures emerging from Marie Claire ‘s Instagram page we can clearly see what a perfect fit she is for the style magazine. In her other two photos, PeeCee’s dressed in Roberto Cavalli and Alexander McQueen and looking so effin’ good! A post shared by Marie Claire (@marieclairemag) on Mar 13, 2017 at 6:37am PDT 
It’s hard not to fall in love with this girl… Agree? A post shared by Marie Claire (@marieclairemag) on Mar 13, 2017 at 10:13am PDT 0
